    "image_with_text_rPVK8b": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_ymVgbd": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Prints Full of Character"
          }
        },
        "text_RDa4Jp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Luna Stripe</strong> appears in a strong blue and cream, bringing the iconic beach, summer feel to the table. Effortlessly easy to layer with other patterns and pieces.</p><p>Meanwhile, <strong>Peony Urn</strong> takes inspiration from Victorian conservatories and hothouses filled with terracotta pots, climbing blooms and beautifully weathered wicker furniture. Rich in detail and romance, the design captures the charm of English garden rooms and the joy of abundant summer flowers.</p><p>There is also a subtle nod to the Bloomsbury set - their creative gatherings, indoor picnics and lives lived between cultivated gardens and grand country houses. All adding an artistic, bohemian spirit to the collection.</p>",
            "code": ""
          }
        },
