        "text_4E44Xb": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Whether you’re hosting a long outdoor lunch, a spontaneous garden supper or simply laying the table for everyday moments, these pieces are designed to be layered, mixed and enjoyed throughout the season.</p><p>The collection is joyful by nature - uplifting colours, expressive prints and thoughtful details that invite people to slow down, gather together and celebrate the beauty of summer living.</p><p>We hope it brings a little extra joy to your table this season.</p>",
